": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before the competitions got underway, the Seine fell under scrutiny over its water quality, resulting in the cancellations of multiple swimming practices and a delay.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 655, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999997610723598, \"rank\": 1.5404147218725017e-07, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competitions\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"scrutiny\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"its water quality\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 703}, {\"ngram\": \"the cancellations\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple swimming practices\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"a delay\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We knew so many people would have asked questions.\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many people\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we were prepared for that.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I will just say, we swam in worse rivers sometimes, like in Tokyo, I do not think it was that great.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9988307614858708, \"rank\": 0.0011699592981433188, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"worse rivers\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And no one was sick.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We raced in the Seine the year before for the test event, and no one was sick after that,\\\" Beaugrand told reporters.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1005, \"end\": 1010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999997610723598, \"rank\": 1.5404147218725017e-07, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the test event\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"Beaugrand\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I knew that we would have actually raced, I was very confident about it,\\\" she added \\\"I was very focused on my race.\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my race\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I started knowing that I was racing for the podium when we were in the run, because we were like four girls and I knew that we had a little gap with the others.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1395, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"the run\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"four girls\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"a little gap\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"the others\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I was just trying to grind my teeth and go for it, and just keep believing that I could do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my teeth\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1434}]}, {\"sente